data.description:
This fantastic home features over 2,000 square feet of space and is conveniently located near NAS Pax River as well as dining, shopping, and activities in beautiful Leonardtown and Solomons Island. The main level of the home features a bright and open living and kitchen floor plan with access to the rear deck. Both dining table space and bar seating are possible. Plentiful natural light and nine foot ceilings add even greater appeal. The fully finished basement, consists of a living space with rear yard access, as well as a full bath and Anne made a optional 4th private room with closet. The primary suite, located on the upper level, is a spacious retreat and includes a walk in closet. Two additional bedrooms, the third full bath, and washer/dryer are also located on the upper level of the home.

Owner will pay the homeowner association dues. No smoking in the house.
